// Dragnet [Container]: dragnet-container-2026-1575 — Vulnerable Base Image Pull
// Status: deprecated | Level: high | ID: fc6ffe26-540f-524d-9f65-2cba76c514fe

#event_simpleName=*
| (ImageFileName = *oraclelinux:5* OR ImageFileName = *oraclelinux:6* OR ImageFileName = *redhat/ubi9:*)
| table([timestamp, ComputerName])
| limit(1000)
